title: Flipping Wholesaling Real Estate Upside Down With Bryce McKinley and Chris Chavez
itunes:title: Flipping Wholesaling Real Estate Upside Down With Bryce McKinley and Chris Chavez
description:
Bryce McKinley and Chris Chavez are the co-founders of REI Results Academy and hosts of the Flipping Wholesaling Upside Down podcast. In this episode we talk everything wholesaling.
 
Learn more about Underdog Empowerment here: https://underdogempowerment.com/107
